  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/358a2c051a341b9312dbdf9ddeda6446.poster.avif?t=1724020578\" width=750 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/358a2c051a341b9312dbdf9ddeda6446.webm?t=1724020578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/358a2c051a341b9312dbdf9ddeda6446.mp4?t=1724020578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Spirit Compass has been shattered, tainting the world with dark miasma and ferocious beasts. <br>It is up to the spirits of Arcadia to reunite the lost shards and defeat Ingelica, the deity <br>responsible for breaking the cycle of rebirth!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16 Characters with unique abilities!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traverse through 11 dungeons.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Routes change each run.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock 64 treasures to help on your quest.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Abilities and Characters level up through-out runs, allowing further progression inside dungeons!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/2b2ebdd831b6bbff10905f0dbf40e1e2.poster.avif?t=1724020578\" width=736 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/2b2ebdd831b6bbff10905f0dbf40e1e2.webm?t=1724020578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/2b2ebdd831b6bbff10905f0dbf40e1e2.mp4?t=1724020578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/358a2c051a341b9312dbdf9ddeda6446.poster.avif?t=1724020578\" width=750 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/358a2c051a341b9312dbdf9ddeda6446.webm?t=1724020578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/358a2c051a341b9312dbdf9ddeda6446.mp4?t=1724020578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Spirit Compass has been shattered, tainting the world with dark miasma and ferocious beasts. <br>It is up to the spirits of Arcadia to reunite the lost shards and defeat Ingelica, the deity <br>responsible for breaking the cycle of rebirth!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16 Characters with unique abilities!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traverse through 11 dungeons.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Routes change each run.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock 64 treasures to help on your quest.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Abilities and Characters level up through-out runs, allowing further progression inside dungeons!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/2b2ebdd831b6bbff10905f0dbf40e1e2.poster.avif?t=1724020578\" width=736 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/2b2ebdd831b6bbff10905f0dbf40e1e2.webm?t=1724020578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319300/extras/2b2ebdd831b6bbff10905f0dbf40e1e2.mp4?t=1724020578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
